description.p:
The invention further relates to a method of installing a wall covering, preferably with wall panels according to any of the preceding claims, comprising the steps of:
a. Providing a first wall panel, with first and second coupling parts at least two opposite sides;
b. Attaching the first wall panel to a supporting surface, leaving a second coupling part of the first wall panel accessible;
c. Providing a second wall panel, with first and second coupling parts at least two opposite sides;
d. Placing a first coupling part of the second wall panel in the second coupling part of the first wall panel;
e. Angling in the second wall panel to be aligned with the first panel, leaving a second coupling part of the second wall panel accessible;
f. Optionally repeating steps c-e with a further panel.
